Package io.github.foxyseta.telegrindr.bot.data

Class Range<T extends Comparable<? super T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.foxyseta.telegrindr.bot.data.Range<T>
  • public class Range<T extends Comparable<? super T>>
extends Object
    A Range defines an interval of values. If bot extremes are not-null, the first one must be less or equal than the second.

    1.0.0
